@startuml
title Money Manager - State Diagram (User Session / Login Attempts)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #111827
}

[*] --> LoggedOut

LoggedOut --> Authenticating : submit credentials
Authenticating --> LoggedIn : credentials valid
Authenticating --> LoggedOut : invalid credentials\n(attempts < 4)
Authenticating --> Locked : invalid credentials\n(attempts >= 4)

LoggedIn --> LoggedOut : logout / close app
Locked --> LoggedOut : (admin resets)\n(app restart)

note right of Locked
  In code: UserService.max_attempts = 4
  When exceeded: LoginScreen disables inputs
end note

@enduml

